Articles.Content:
Alright chaps, I'm conceding defeat here. Here's the <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> patch I tried to make to allow me to mess with SSTUVolumeContainer tankageMass quickly and easily:

    @PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[SSTUVolumeContainer]]
    {    
        @MODULE[SSTUVolumeContainer],*
        {
            @tankageMass = 0.037

        }
    }

Cannot for the life of me get the damn thing to work though.
